                <ul class="list-unstyled mt-4">
                    <li class="mb-3">✔️ Xalqaro sug‘urta va favqulodda yordam</li>
                    <li class="mb-3">✔️ O‘zbek tilida doimiy qo‘llab-quvvatlash</li>
                    <li class="mb-3">✔️ Moslashuvchan to‘lov va bron siyosati</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="info-card">
                            <h6>Sayohat rejalari</h6>
