                            <h6>Premium xizmat</h6>
                            <p>VIP transfer, shaxsiy gid va eksklyuziv turlar.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="info-card">
                            <h6>Shaxsiy kabinet</h6>
                            <p>Buyurtmalar holatini real vaqt rejimida ko‘ring.</p>
